== Instructions for release == 

* Update main/conf/iCubVersion.cmake

* Update yarp version info inside admin/scripts/current_dependencies.txt 

* Update licensing info
  Run ./admin/scripts/update-license.sh
  Check main/COPYING_new
  Check main/AUTHORS_new
  cp main/COPYING_new main/COPYING
  cp main/AUTHORS_new main/AUTHORS

* Update main/ChangeLog and ChangeLog with tag notice

* Make tag
  Commit new version, write down revision svn revision number (REVISION)
  
  svn copy -r REVISION https://robotcub.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/robotcub/trunk/iCub https://robotcub.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/robotcub/tags/iCub1.1.8

* Make packages

  ./admin/scripts/icub-package.sh 1.1.8

This will produce inside package-tmp/iCub-main-1.1.8

  iCub-main-src-1.1.8.tar.gz
  iCub-main-src-1.1.8.zip

and will automatically upload them on eris

Update the packages to sourceforge:

  cd package-tmp
  rsync --recursive iCub-main-1.1.8 USERNAME,robotcub@frs.sourceforge.net:/home/frs/project/r/ro/robotcub/iCub-main"
  
  

